title: Bass Explosion USA - Vol. 1 (320kbps)
description:
Bass Explosion USA is a stellar collection of first-class funky bass singles and is a 
good introduction to this hip-hop/dance subgenre.


Very rare old school collection in the 90's presenting the best in bass.

20 booming hi-tech digital bass tracks from the world's best acts.

Bass 305, Bass syndicate, Techno bass crew, Bass invaders, Euro bass express, Bass gangster, Bass alliance, Bass metal heads, Bass destroyers, 808xs, Bass death metal squad, Mc magic mark, Bass enforcers, Bass bombers.
